              <additions>
                <p/>
                <list>
                  <item xml:id="p1addition1" n="1">
                    <locus from="56a"/>
                    <p>On fol. 56 a is the following note in a good Arabic hand:</p>
                    <p>
                    <quote xml:lang="ar">
                        <choice>
                          <sic>نضر</sic>
                          <corr resp="http://syriaca.org/documentation/editors.xml#wwright">(نظر)</corr>
                        </choice> في هذا الكتاب واحد خاطي وكتب منه شيءِ <foreign xml:lang="en">(sic)</foreign> قليل عن الاخبار الاوله</quote>
                  </p>
                  </item>
                  <item xml:id="p1addition2" n="2">
                    <locus from="56b"/>
                    <p>On fol. 56 b is an older Syriac note, stating that the book
                                        once belonged to a priest named <persName>Yāyē</persName>: </p>
                    <p>
                                        <quote xml:lang="syr">ܐܝܬܘܗܝ ܟܬܒܐ ܗܢܐ ܕܝܐܝܐ ܩܫܝܫܐ ܕܝܪܝܐ
                                            ܐܟܣܢܝܐ ܟܠ ܕܩܪܐ ܨܠܐ.</quote>
                                    </p>
                  </item>
                </list>
